          <div class="page-summary-wrap" role="note" aria-label="Business summary">
            <p class="page-summary"><strong>Hunting season storage in Vernal Utah</strong>. Fort Knox Self Storage offers mouse-proof steel containers to protect rifles, bows, camp equipment, and hunting gear. 24/7 access, from <strong>$130/month</strong>. <strong>2225 South 3250 East, Vernal, UT 84078</strong>. Call <a href="tel:4358287710">435-828-7710</a>.</p>
            <span class="page-summary-meta">Last updated: <time datetime="2026-04-08">April 2026</time></span>
          </div>
          <div class="voice-answer-block">
            <p><strong>Need storage for hunting gear in Vernal?</strong> Fort Knox Self Storage has mouse-proof steel containers starting at $130 per month with 24/7 access. Call James at 435-828-7710.</p>
          </div>
